*** FreeLoader - FEATURES ***

** Robot actions **
- Mouse actions
	-- move to location
		[assign random error margin to coordinates]
		[use relative coordinates?]
		[
			plot path, [assign smoothness, [randomize smoothness]]
		]
		[human mode?]
	-- click / hold / release
		[
			repeat click?, 
			[
				assign number of clicks, [randomize number],
				assign interval, [randomize intervals],
				randomize click length?
			]
		]
		[
			assign hold length, [randomize length]
		]
	-- scroll
		[assign scroll direction]
		[assign scroll speed]
		[repeat scroll?, [assign number of scrolls, [randomize number], assign interval, [randomize intervals]]]
	/*-- perform a move set
		[repeat move set?, [assign number of repeats, [randomize number], assign interval, [randomize intervals]]]*/
- Keystrokes
	-- press / hold / release
		[repeat press?, [assign number of repeats, [randomize number], assign interval, [randomize intervals]]]
		[assign hold length, [randomize length]]
	-- use a shortcut
		[randomize intervals between shortcut key presses?]
	-- type text
		[
			press each key separately?,
				[
					assign interval between presses, [randomize interval],
					separate interval between words?, [randomize interval]
				]
			insta-type?
		]
- Wait
	-- assign waiting time
		[randomize waiting time]
- Jump to action line
	-- assign line number
		[choose random line in range]
- Run a program from cmd
	-- assign program path
		

** User options **
- Robot
	-- create a robot
	-- scrap a robot
	-- start a robot
	-- interrupt a robot
	-- resume a robot
	-- shutdown a robot
- Record user actions
	-- set recording polling rate
	-- set recording hot-keys
- Robot action
	-- add a robot action
	-- delete a robot action
	-- modify a robot action
	-- create / edit / remove a keyboard shortcut
	-- create / edit / remove an action set
	
